radiographic_examinations.findings: Fluid collection extending from the electrostimulator to the left side of the rectouterine pouch.
radiographic_examinations.changes_over_time: A subsequent CT scan showed a pelvic fluid collection posterior to the vagina and the uterus measuring 13x9 cm. Two weeks later, another CT scan showed recurrence of the fluid collection posterior to the vagina and the uterus, now measuring 11.5x8x7 cm.
